official_title: A bill to amend the Act of October 27, 1972, establishing the Golden Gate National Recreation Area in San Francisco and Marin Counties, Calif., and for other purposes.

summary.text: Establishes the Golden Gate National Recreation Area in San Francisco and Marin Counties, California, and sets forth properties to be included in the Area.
